    #Information_Technology-section-one.DevOps_Manager
      %p= l('[_1]’s IT Operations Group is responsible for the design, development and operation of the company’s high-traffic networks. Its responsibilities include hardware and software deployment, up-time and reliability testing, incident response reporting, network security, intrusion detection, and load balancing.', stash->{website_name})
